Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:24.24,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Yu-ki-to!}Yukito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.37,Main,Alural,0,0,0,,{Mitama-chan.}Mitama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:27.41,Main,Alural,0,0,0,,{It's dangerous to jump onto him like that.}Bahaya langsung lompat 'gitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:28.22,Main - Top,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Yukito!}Yukito!
