Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:29.49,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{Will do.}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:34.83,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{Uh, that wasn't it, was it?}Eng, bukan yang barusan itu, 'kan?
