Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.34,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{This can't be...}Jangan bilang ....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:39.91,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{I don't believe it.}Tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.83,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{How can I have so few followers?}Pengikutku tidak ada?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:48.34,Sign_Basic,Face,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(332,130)\an8\c&H000000&\3c&H8F928F&\shad0\b1\fs36\t(2822,3822,1 \3c&H28B2B4&)}{God}Dewa
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:44.53,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{The more followers a god has,}Kekuatan dewa, tuh, semakin kuat ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:47.24,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{the more powerful they become.}... seiring bertambahnya pengikut.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:50.43,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{But you can't do anything if \Nyou've got zero followers.}Kalau pengikutnya nol, tak bisa apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:52.92,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{We're in an alternate world!}Ini isekai, lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:55.31,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{Why did you think you'd \Nhave any followers here?!}Mana mungkin ada pengikutmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.02,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Why are you talking like that suddenly?}Kenapa tiba-tiba nyerocos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:59.43,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Besides, how come it's zero? What about you?}Terus, nol, tuh, maksudnya apa?!\NKalau kamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:00.42,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{I can't believe this!}Bohong, 'kan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:04.23,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{I used the last of my \Npowers to save your life!}Aku pakai sisa kekuatanku \Nuntuk menyelamatkanmu, lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:03.85,Main - Top,Guy,0,0,0,,{This is bad!}Gawat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:05.34,Main - Top,Guy,0,0,0,,{The people from the Imperial capital}Orang-orang ibu kota Kekaisaran ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:06.82,Main - Top,Guy,0,0,0,,{have started to investigate that incident!}... sepertinya sudah mulai menyelidiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.77,Main,Guy1,0,0,0,,{Doesn't that mean that soldiers \Nare going to show up here, too?}Berarti mereka akan ke desa ini juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.01,Main,Guy2,0,0,0,,{That would be bad.}Gawat, nih.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.61,Main,Guy2,0,0,0,,{Maybe we shouldn't be drinking.}Bukan waktunya minum ....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:13.55,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{No worries!}Tenang saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.83,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{Yukito will sort it out again somehow!}Yukito pasti akan \Nlakukan sesuatu lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:16.57,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{Right?}Ya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:19.46,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{Yeah, of course.}A-Ah, iya, tentu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:21.24,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{Told you so!}Tuh, 'kan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.23,Main - Top,Guy1,0,0,0,,{I knew he'd come through.}Gile ... Yukito memang hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:24.94,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{We got this, no problem!}Sip! Gas, gas, gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:25.80,Main - Top,Guy2,0,0,0,,{The Imperial Army can bring it on!}Sini maju lu, Prajurit Kekaisaran!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:29.33,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{This'll be a piece of cake! Woo!}Gampang, gampang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:32.77,Italics,Yukito,0,0,0,,{This is bad.}Gawat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.79,Italics,Yukito,0,0,0,,{This is really bad.}Serius gawat, dah, ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:39.60,Italics,Yukito,0,0,0,,{Now what do I do?!}Harus 'gimana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.52,Italics,Yukito,0,0,0,,{At this rate...}Kalau terus begini ....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:45.84,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{It's mean to just leave me there.}Jahat banget ninggalin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.62,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{How dare you do that to a god...?}Padahal ke dewa ....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:54.36,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.95,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{It was a reflex... No, screw that!}Reflek ... Eh, bukan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.20,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{Stop following me everywhere!}Jangan ngikutin aku terus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.93,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{But you were acting weird.}Habis, kamu aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.07,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{What's wrong?}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:03.76,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{There's nothing I can do.}Tak ada yang bisa kulakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.84,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{Because of me,}Gegara aku,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:09.55,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{this village might be attacked and destroyed.}desa ini mungkin akan \Ndihancurkan para prajurit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:10.67,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Really?}Hee ....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:14.64,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Then the two of us should run away right now!}Kalau 'gitu, kita \Ntinggal kabur sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:16.35,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{I'm not going to do that!}Mana bisa begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.95,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{I can't just do nothing and run away again.}Tak melakukan apa pun dan kabur lagi ....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:23.85,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{That's...}Itu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.37,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{What's so wrong about running away?}Memang apa salahnya kabur?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.37,0:09:30.82,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{I've watched you from the beginning.}Aku selalu memperhatikanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.28,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{You always gave your best,}Kamu selalu berjuang,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:34.41,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{always kept enduring...}dan selalu menahan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:37.54,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{So you're just going to do that again?}Kamu berniat melakukan hal yang sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:38.20,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{No.}Bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:41.60,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{I just let things happen to me.}Aku hanya mengabaikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:44.10,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{By the sect... by my dad...}Baik sekte, ayahku ....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.29,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{I kept running away from \Nputting up resistance.}Aku terus kabur dari menentang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:50.29,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{And we saw how that turned out for me.}Dan inilah hasilnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:51.17,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{Damn it!}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:54.85,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{Mitama.}Mitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:57.13,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{If you get some followers,}Kalau manusia yang \Njadi pengikutmu bertambah,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:10:00.68,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{you'll be able to use your godly powers, right?}kamu jadi bisa \Npakai kekuatan dewa, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:03.19,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{I mean, yeah.}Ah, iya, sih ....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:06.27,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{Then I will make you a god.}Kalau begitu, aku \Nakan menjadikanmu dewa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.02,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:11.12,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{I am going to create "religion" \Nand "God" in this world.}Aku akan ciptakan agama \Ndan dewa di dunia ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:18.46,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{I won't just stand by and do nothing \Nlike in the previous world.}Aku takkan tinggal diam dan \Nberakhir seperti di dunia sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:25.60,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{You'll do anything I say, right?}Kamu akan dengarkan \Nsemua perkataanku, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.93,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{Of... of course!}Te-Tentu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:32.84,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{I am your "follower"!}Hamba ini pengikut Mitama-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:37.14,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{I will lick anywhere you ask, with pleasure!}Izinkan hamba \Nmenjilat dengan senang hati!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:39.72,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Good boy.}Anak baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:44.87,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Such a wonderful servant deserves a reward.}Pelayan manut harus diberi hadiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:03.01,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{Roy, are you listening?}Hei, kau dengar tidak?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:11.13,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I'll become a follower.}Aku mau jadi pengikut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:12.76,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{Good.}Sip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:15.85,Sign_Basic,txt,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnTimes New Roman\b1\c&HBCFDFF&\bord4\shad0\3c&H3E455A&}{Followers}Pengikut
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:15.84,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Yay, we got one!}Asyik, nambah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.12,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Wait, how come you're not a follower?!}Eh, kenapa kamu nggak jadi pengikut?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:20.43,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Hey, Yukito! You listening?!}Hei, Yukito, dengar nggak, sih?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.62,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Hey, Yukito!}Hei, Yukito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:23.71,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Why?! Why?!}Kenapa? Kenapa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:23.71,Main - Top,Yukito,0,0,0,,{Because you're like this!}Yah, karena inilah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:25.44,Main - Top,Yukito,0,0,0,,{Stop, get off!}Hentikan! Turun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:26.15,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Yukito!}Yukito! Hei, Yukito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:30.17,Main,Alural,0,0,0,,{What's up, Chilchil?}Ada apa, Chilchil?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.53,Main,Alural,0,0,0,,{There, there.}Cup, cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:35.07,Main - Top,Yukito,0,0,0,,{So starting today,}Jadi,
