Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:38.73,Main - Top,Yukito,0,0,0,,{we are going to spread a religion \Nthat worships Mitama as its god.}mulai hari ini, kita akan sebarkan agama \Nyang menyembah Mitama sebagai dewa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:42.62,Main - Top,Yukito,0,0,0,,{If possible, I'd like to get us 10,000 \Nfollowers before the army comes and attacks.}Setidaknya, kuingin dapat 10.000 pengikut \Nsebelum prajurit menyerang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:44.22,Main - Top,Mitama,0,0,0,,{With that many followers,}Kalau ada pengikut sebanyak itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:47.39,Main - Top,Mitama,0,0,0,,{I could reduce cities to ashes \Nor even split oceans in two.}aku bahkan bisa hanguskan kota \Njadi abu maupun membelah lautan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:51.00,Main - Top,Roy,0,0,0,,{I want to spread Mitama-sama's \Ncuteness and her toe holy water!}Aku ingin sebarkan keimutan \NMitama-sama dan air suci kakinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:56.01,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{Performing actual miracles is the most \Neffective way to amass followers...}Menunjukkan keajaiban ialah cara paling \Nefektif untuk dapatkan pengikut, tapi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:59.18,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{But right now, she's a \Nshell of her former glory.}dia yang sekarang itu cuma keroco.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.98,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{We'll start off with a speech.}Yang jelas, mulai dari pidato dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:08.02,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{My shitty dad taught me how to \Nwrite speeches that excite followers,}Ayahku yang menyebalkan sudah mengajari \Ncara buat pidato yang menarik hati pengikut,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:09.19,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{so I'll put together a draft, and...}jadi nanti kubuat kerangkanya ....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:10.64,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{That won't be necessary.}Tidak perlu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:13.39,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Even without the power to perform miracles,}Tanpa kekuatan untuk \Ntunjukkan keajaiban pun ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:17.67,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{I've got godly wisdom that I gained by \Nhaving lived over ten billion years.}... aku punya berkah ilahi yang didapat \Ndengan hidup lebih dari 10 miliar tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:20.41,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{I'll use it to impress the extent \Nof my powers upon the humans.}Akan kupakai berkah itu untuk \Nsampaikan kekuatan pada manusia ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:23.79,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Then they'll have no choice \Nbut to kneel before me!}... dan membuat mereka bersujud!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:25.16,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Pray to me!}Berdoalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:28.68,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{I've been alive ever since \Nthe universe was created,}Aku sudah hidup sejak \Nalam semesta diciptakan, jadi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.12,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{so pray to me!}berdoalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.01,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{I know absolutely everything!}Aku tahu segalanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:34.88,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{If you want to know what I know,}Kalau ingin tahu yang kutahu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:36.50,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{pray to me!}maka berdoalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:38.72,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Take Yukito over here!}Yang ada di sini ialah Yukito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:41.51,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{I know that the very first \Nword he uttered wasn't "Mom",}Kata yang paling pertama \Ndia ucap bukanlah "Mama",
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:43.87,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{but "Mitama-sama".}melainkan "Mitama-sama".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:48.73,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Or that he used to call broccoli "buccoroli".}Atau nyebut brokoli dengan "bukkorori".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:50.62,Flashback,Young Yukito,0,0,0,,{Buccoroli.}Bukkorori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:54.23,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Or that the birthmark on his right \Nbutt cheek isn't a birthmark,}Lalu tanda di pantat kanannya itu \Nbukanlah tanda lahir,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:57.90,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{but a piece of embedded pencil lead!}melainkan ujung pensil! \NSeperti itulah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:01.45,Main,Alural,0,0,0,,{You were so cute.}Kamu lucu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:04.26,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Let's see, what else do I know about Yukito?}Eng, terus Yukito ....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:07.23,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{Enough speeches.}Pidatonya sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:10.50,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{I was wrong. Gods really \Nhave to perform miracles.}Dewa memang harus tunjukkan keajaiban.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:14.92,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{B-But I don't have my powers yet.}Ta-Tapi aku belum punya kekuatan ....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:16.81,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{I know that.}Tahu, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.76,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{I'm not counting on you anymore.}Aku takkan mengandalkanmu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.84,Main,Yukito,0,0,0,,{I'll have to do this all myself.}Akan kulakukan semuanya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:23.54,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{Mitama-sama has done no wrong!\NI think this dopey act is adorable.}Mitama-sama tidak salah, \Nsi bodoh inilah yang lucu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:24.10,Main,Mitama,0,0,0,,{Dopey?!}Bodoh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:32.65,Main,Alural,0,0,0,,{U-Um, so what are you doing?}A-Anu, mau ngapain?
